## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Set up database
cp .env.example .env
npx prisma migrate dev --name init

# Run development server
npm run dev
```

{% if use_docker %}
## Docker

```bash
docker compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up -d
```
{% endif %}

